Show creators Matthew Mercer, Marisha Ray, Sam Riegel, Taliesin Jaffe, Travis Willingham, and Liam O'Brien sit down with showrunner Tasha Huo and voice of The Ruby of the Sea, Anika Noni Rose, to discuss the making of the show.

Join the cast & executive producers of The Mighty Nein as they explore the creative process behind adapting Critical Role’s Campaign 2 to animation. This talkback series will dive into all the behind the scenes details with special guests for each segment.
